
Module TeX::DVI:

	Low level methods to write out DVI (DeVice Independent) file,
	the default output format of the TeX typesetting file.

Installation:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make install

Use:

	use TeX::DVI;
	my $dvi = new TeX::DVI "texput.dvi";
	$dvi->preamble();
	$dvi->begin_page();


